headline: How the Genuine Parts Story Is Evolving as Analysts Rethink the Outlook
summary: Genuine Parts stock has seen its fair value estimate tick up from $144.78 to $146.11 per share, accompanied by a modest decrease in the discount rate to 7.70%. This change comes amid a fresh wave of analyst research that highlights both improving trends in the company’s core industries and some remaining caution regarding broader economic uncertainty.
